headline: Match Group to Reinvest $45M in 2025, Focuses on Gen Z and Tinder Upgrades
summary: Evercore ISI kept its In-Line rating and $32 price target for Match Group Inc. (NASDAQ:MTCH) on May 21. According to the firm’s analysis, Match Group intends to reinvest $45 million of its $100 million in cost savings in fiscal year 2025.
